s with top brands, designers, architects and organizations. These partnerships open doors to exclusive job opportunities and provide our students with a competitive edge in the job market.<\/p><p><strong><span class=\"blue\">Alumni Success:\u00a0<\/span><\/strong>Our alumni network is a testament to our commitment to excellence. Graduates of NIF GLOBAL, Kondhwa in Pune have gone on to secure prestigious positions at leading design houses, start their own successful labels, and make significant contributions to the fashion industry.<\/p><p><strong><span class=\"blue\">Campus Recruitment Drives:<\/span><\/strong>\u00a0We host annual recruitment drives on campus, inviting renowned brands and companies to interview our students. These events provide a platform for students to showcase their talent and secure job offers before graduation.<\/p><p><strong><span class=\"blue\">Continuous Learning and Development:<\/span>\u00a0<\/strong>We believe in fostering a culture of continuous learning. Our students have access to workshops, seminars, and guest lectures by industry stalwarts, ensuring they stay ahead of the curve and are always industry-ready.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Welcome To NIF Kondhwa At NIF Kondhwa design education is top-notch and relevant. We are Pune\u2019s No. 1 design institute; [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_eb_attr":"","site-sidebar-layout":"no-sidebar","site-content-layout":"plain-container","ast-site-content-layout":"full-width-container","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site-post-title":"di